---
---
<section id="por-que-nexus" class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden bg-cosmos-dark border-t border-gray-800">
  <!-- Subtle star overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-stars opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Left Column: Logo (Monumental scale, transparent, tilted, centered) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex items-center justify-center relative select-none">
        <img src="/logo-pegasus-only.png" alt="Pegasus Icon" class="w-[250%] sm:w-[350%] lg:w-[550%] max-w-none object-contain -rotate-[15deg] drop-shadow-[0_0_80px_rgba(255,255,255,0.4)] transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-105 hover:-rotate-[20deg] relative z-0" />
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Manifesto text -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-6 text-left relative z-10">
        <!-- Huge Watermark text in the background -->
        <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[10rem] sm:text-[14rem] lg:text-[18rem] font-bold text-gray-800/[0.02] select-none pointer-events-none font-montserrat tracking-widest z-0">NEXUS</div>
        
        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <h2 class="text-gold-deep text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-glow relative z-10">Filosofía de Trabajo</h2>
        
        <!-- Main Title -->
        <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-normal font-heading text-white tracking-wide leading-tight relative z-10">
          ¿Por qué <span class="text-cosmos-blue italic font-semibold text-glow">Pegasus Nexus</span>?
        </h3>
        
        <!-- Divider Line -->
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gold-deep/50 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(136,192,208,0.8)] relative z-10"></div>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-300 font-montserrat font-light leading-relaxed relative z-10">
          Combinamos experiencia en gestión empresarial, Business Intelligence, automatización e inteligencia artificial para diseñar soluciones que generan resultados medibles. No desarrollamos software por desarrollar; creamos herramientas estratégicas que impulsan tu crecimiento.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Two Columns of Features -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 pt-4 relative z-10">
          
          <!-- Point 1 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6 text-cosmos-blue text-glow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" fill="currentColor" fill-opacity="0.2"/>
                <circle cx="12" cy="5" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
                <circle cx="5" cy="17" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
                <circle cx="19" cy="17" r="2" fill="currentColor"/>
                <line x1="12" y1="7" x2="12" y2="9"/>
                <line x1="6.5" y1="15.5" x2="10.5" y2="12.5"/>
                <line x1="17.5" y1="15.5" x2="13.5" y2="12.5"/>
              </svg>
              <h4 class="text-base font-montserrat font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">El Negocio Primero</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-montserrat font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
              Nuestro enfoque no comienza con la tecnología. Comienza entendiendo la lógica de tu negocio y tus objetivos de crecimiento.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Point 2 -->
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="w-6 h-6 text-cosmos-blue text-glow" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/>
                <polyline points="7.5 10 11 14 17 8"/>
              </svg>
              <h4 class="text-base font-montserrat font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wider">Decisiones Inteligentes</h4>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-montserrat font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
               Porque una empresa no necesita más sistemas que dupliquen tareas. Necesita mejores datos para tomar decisiones seguras.
            </p>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
